Subject: Mail list help

This is an automatic help system of {domain} service. 
All commands wil be send to the service through email messages, and the
response will be email messages either, no need of web pages or any 
other tool rathern than your email.

The mail list service supports following commands:

help@{domain}                            This help
subscribe-[mail list name]@{domain}      Subscribe to a mail list
unsubscribe-[mail list name]@{domain}    Unsubscribe of a mail list
members-[mail list name]@{domain}        Return members subscribed to a list

To send a message to the list simply ... send it to the [mail list name]@{domain}


